PROBLEM :
Sort the elements in ascending order by using bubble sort

HOW I IMPLEMENTED THIS ?
Here I have used Bubble Sorting algorithm to sort those elements in ascending order.
In bubble sort algorithm, array is traversed from first element to last element. 
Here, current element is compared with the next element. 
If current element is greater than the next element, it is swapped.

TIME COMPLEXITY OF BUBBLE SORT ALGORITHM
BEST CASE : O(n)
AVERAGE CASE : O(n^2)
WORST CASE : O(n^2)

WORST SPACE COMPLEXITY : O(1)

STABILITY OF BUBBLE SORT ALGORITHM : Yes

TEST CASE 1 :
  INPUT :
    Enter array size
    6
    Enter elements into array
    21  24  2  -8  14  6
  OUTPUT :
    Array Before Bubble Sort
    21  24  2  -8  14  6
    Array After Bubble Sort
    -8  2  6  14  21  24
    
    
TEST CASE 2 :
  INPUT :
    Enter array size
    5
    Enter elements into array
    2  1  7  5  8
  OUTPUT :
    Array Before Bubble Sort
    2  1  7  5  8
    Array After Bubble Sort
    1  2  5  7  8
    
    
TEST CASE 3 :
  INPUT :
    Enter array size
    3
    Enter elements into array
    3  3  3
  OUTPUT :
    Array Before Bubble Sort
    3  3  3
    Array After Bubble Sort
    3  3  3
    
    
